Open preferences then 'Sharing'

click on file sharing then add folder

then you can select your users

in case you want Guests to access set 'Everyone' o 'Guest' in users
and read or read/write if you need

(alternative you can access with your account or generally with
any account that is available in the 'Users and Groups' settings )

in case you want to use guest you need to go to users then click on
'Guest' and check if 'Allow shared folder' is enabled.

now you can access from other machine to the mac with Guest

in Windows if it asks for a username and password
just type as username 'guest' and you are done
